/usr/share/doc/dovecot-1.0/examples/dovecot-sql.conf

CentOS 5
dovecot-1.0-1.2.rc15.el5
dovecot俞outlock 一直o法到C密a
用 telnet localhost 110 ]看到 +ok Dovecot ready        然後就停住了

教酷W@後_maillognlF
libraries: libsepol.so.1: failed to map segment from shared object: Cannot allocate memory
於是作了以下幼
#vi /etc/dovecot.conf
找到@一行
＃login_process_size = 32    
把＃拿掉 改
login_process_size = 64
再绦
# /etc/init.d/dovecot restart
y看看
# telnet localhost 110 
Trying 127.0.0.1...
Connected to localhost.localdomain (127.0.0.1).
Escape character is '^]'.
+OK Dovecot ready.
成功解Q
⒖季W站    http://www.cyberciti.biz/tips/rhel-dovecot-error-while-loading-shared-libraries.html
